      "content": "I believe religious groups should be allowed to opt-out of government mandates that conflict with their beliefs, as this protects the fundamental right to religious freedom. While the state must remain secular in its operations, it cannot force individuals to violate their conscience or faith. Protecting religious liberty is essential to a free society, and allowing opt-outs ensures that the government does not become an instrument of religious coercion.",
